Enum NavigationCue.TriggerMode

    NavigationCue

    public static enum NavigationCue.TriggerMode
extends java.lang.Enum<NavigationCue.TriggerMode>
    Defines how the cue should be triggered--based on distance away from a point or estimated time until the point is reached. For now, only distance is supported.
